description:
Visioneers are humans who developed a special relation to machines. Living in a sort of symbiosis, they are connected with all of her five senses to them.
Most of them live in Junk Castle, a district of Old Tokyo; only a small part of them, including http://anidb.net/ch13447 [Lebia Maverick], are integrated into human society.
Their existence was detected by http://anidb.net/ch25760 [Stefan L. Maverick].
name: Visioneers
